Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.59,0:02:45.51,ep-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1300,0)\be1}The Light of the Eyelids
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:47.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:50.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do your eyes still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Biki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:53.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the only one I'm going to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,why I'm sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:05.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are Mushi in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:07.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:11.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've always been there in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sui is the youngest daughter of the head family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:23.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,About half a year ago, she developed\Na sickness that made her eyes hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:32.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a strange sickness, and no eye doctor\Ncould figure out what caused it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:38.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before they could find a treatment, the smallest\Nbit of light would cause her eyes pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:49.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was left with my family to hide in the dark shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:54.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It may have been the best thing to do for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:58.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it seemed to me as if she\Nwas being abandoned here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:17.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's another set of eyelids behind our eyelids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:27.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a place where light can never reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's where the Mushi are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Second eyelids?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:32.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know how to close them, Biki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:46.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's flickering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's moving in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:58.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:03.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you shut your eyelids, your eyes\Nare still watching your eyelids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:05.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't really closed your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:12.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when you want {\i1}real{\i0} darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:17.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,you close your eyes {\i1}again{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:25.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then {\i1}true{\i0} darkness sets in from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:43.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure are clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:01.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We play in the deep darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:08.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't really see anything when you enter the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:14.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But after a while, things start to show their\Nform on the other side of the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:22.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come I can see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's pitch black in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:29.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because there's a stream of light beneath the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:31.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:35.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can see it if you close your second eyelids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you watch the true darkness for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:44.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You start to see specks of light in the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they start to overflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:54.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you look carefully, you'd see that they're all Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:58.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I try to go closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:02.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:12.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't go any closer to the stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't even know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:22.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A one-eyed man is always there to say\Nthat from the other side of the stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:27.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I always watch from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:57.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The things Sui sees with her eyes shut...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Biki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:13.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're staying in the shed for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I burned her old blindfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:19.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I disinfected both my hands and the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:29.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't mean you won't get infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:35.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The head family abandoned her because\Nthey were afraid of that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:39.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:42.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a very good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to bear with it, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:09:01.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay with her so that she doesn't\Nlose the light in her soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:05.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:10.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,don't fall to the same illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:15.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:19.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:17.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:20.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:25.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:56.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Biki,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,are you still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:04.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Biki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:16.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Biki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:21.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Biki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:26.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,not letting Biki come anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He contracted your illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:50.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:55.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He shouldn't have been so compassionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:15.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you open the door, Biki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:19.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm an expert in this field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:30.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gave him medication and painkillers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:34.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll get worse if you leave him in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:39.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Ginko, a Mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard rumors about the girl in the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:56.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eye doctors can't handle it;\Nyou have to ask for us Mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:01.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Biki... will Biki be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:05.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it hasn't been long since his Mushi hatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:09.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Medicinal treatment should do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:19.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Biki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:23.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Biki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Biki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:34.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:40.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:42.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sui!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:51.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do your eyes still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:13:59.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good, it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:08.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sui's sickness is caused by something\Ncalled Manako-no-Yamimushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They breed in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:17.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You stayed with Sui in the dark for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know Sui?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:23.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,One-eyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:30.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:28.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was there when I closed my second eyelids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:35.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The light in that stream isn't of the\Nsame substance as light on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:38.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's poisonous to the eyes to look at it up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:41.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has a left eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:45.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe he's not the person Sui was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to start treatment on Sui after sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:53.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:55.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sui.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:26.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you not to go into that stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sui...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:59.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sui's eyes are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:10.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your eyeballs get consumed by the darkness when\Nyou close your second eyelids for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right then, Sui.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to lure the Mushi out with the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:23.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Slowly open your eyes with your second eyelids closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:46.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come out, Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mushi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:25.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:28.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sui, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:57.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:02.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now for Sui's eyeballs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:04.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:08.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bugs in her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, they're no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if this'll work, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm giving this to Sui.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to stop freaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:31.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Relax. It's just an artificial eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:34.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the liquefied Mushi from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:40.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll turn even a glass ball into an eyeball.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:54.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That stream of light that the two of you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:00.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Close your second eyelids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:05.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:09.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the path to darkness will be opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:15.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used to be like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:32.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is said that man forgot how to close his\Nsecond eyelids once he found light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:39.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But those who lived may have been better off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:49.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For it is said that many have lost\Nsight by watching {\i1}it{\i0} for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second eyelids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,True darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:02.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Light of a different nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:18.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The swarm of {\i1}countless essences of\Nlife{\i0} swimming beneath our feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:25.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It got really bright all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:28.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then it was pitch black again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:36.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then my feet fell through, and I could\Nsee the light flowing way down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:43.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was only for a brief moment right after\Nthat Mushi-shi put that eye in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:47.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it was really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:49.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt like I was being drawn in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wished I could watch it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:20:59.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:05.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sui left the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:10.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She sees trees, flowers, light.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:18.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll never be seduced by that strange\Nlight in the darkness again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:28.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that man lost his real\Nleft eye the same way Sui did.
